    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a long, vine-like whip covered in thorns that lashes out at your command toward a creature in range. Make a melee spell attack against the target. If the attack hits, the creature takes [[/r 1d6]] piercing damage, and if the creature is Large or smaller, you pull the creature up to 10 feet closer to you.</p><h3>At Higher Levels</h3><p>This spells damage increases by 1d6 when you reach 5th level (2d6), 11th level (3d6), and 17th level (4d6).</p><p><strong>Spell Lists.</strong> Artificer, Druid</p>",
